  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Samurai Jack is a warrior who is banished by the shape-shifting wizard Aku into the bizarre and twisted future. Bearing his new futuristic name, Jack wanders the land searching for a portal back in time to right the wrongs of the past. He has learned of a mysterious Amulet that, when all its pieces are found, will enable him to return to the past.. Join Samurai Jack on a journey of honor and revenge through a futuristic world filled with wonders and help him rid the world of evil once and for all.",
